{"tid":1374440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"乖啦 口罩眼罩頭盔著長褲啊！","createTime":"2019-07-27T18:44:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T10:57:20.000Z","uid":30822,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7608dc16c687ceb3921a43ef862eadba4c823ef1","tid":1374440,"uid":30822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:44:32.000Z","msg":"由6.9開始到7.27都有好多次活動<br />\n但直到今次7.27都仲係有班人未生性<br />\n出到黎 呢最基本既口罩都冇<br />\n有啲女仔戴哂眼罩頭盔加豬咀<br />\n但就著住背心短褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能你會話戴口罩著長褲好熱好焗<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但你乖啦 依加係出黎抗爭啊<br />\n唔係去户外學習日啊</span><br />\n出得黎遊行定發夢 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔理你係前線定後排 <br />\n都要有隨時會受傷既心理準備</span><br />\n著返合適既衣著同裝備真係咁難咩？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">其實你地肯做少少野保護返自己<br />\n已經係減輕緊first acid既負擔</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以每個人都自備定口罩眼罩頭盔！<br />\n有豬咀就更好啦！<br />\n絲打們就乖乖地著返長褲啦！</span></span>"},{"pid":"b3db3393210ddc0b78a743414e3fd745838a584e","tid":1374440,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:53:30.000Z","msg":"「長文」抗爭除Be Water外，Assassin's Creed嘅信條你都一定要識！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1374405\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1374405</a>"},{"pid":"ff544989898b2d7d8d161ad954efc84fff46aab9","tid":1374440,"uid":76592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:14:03.000Z","msg":"前線人員？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油！"},{"pid":"5feaefc35e6e9acb48aa7b8e56b8e8310917f6e2","tid":1374440,"uid":30822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ff544989898b2d7d8d161ad954efc84fff46aab9","tid":1374440,"uid":76592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:14:03.000Z","msg":"前線人員？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:45:18.000Z","msg":"唔算係企得